{"title":"犟牛","authors":["刘岚山"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":7,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"犟牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘岚山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病中读四川奉节青年美术工作者魏靖宇的阴沉木树根造型艺术《犟牛》，感而题诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还没有倒下的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你总是高昂着头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆睁一双眼珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望着长天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然瘦骨嶙峋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不减犟牛的脾气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不信，就请敲打吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满耳是钢铁的交响；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然满身结结疤疤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不自愧也不自炫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经历过大风大浪的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就应该更加纯朴、真实；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管轭头有多重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管太阳何时落山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不管还有多少待耕地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从不叫喊、不叹气……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要还立在大地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就不肯安安静静；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尾巴早已经翘起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管人家怎么说法。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}